<subSubSection id="C33F6520EE0DFFCDFCCAF93EFA0B52B3" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE0DFFCDFCCAF93EFCC45254" blockId="4.[811,1456,1779,2028]" box="[813,878,1779,1805]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">NOTE</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE0DFFCDFCCAF8DFFA0B52B3" blockId="4.[811,1456,1779,2028]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">
This species is morphologically close to 
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0DFFCDFB22F8DEFC655213" authority="(C. K. Schneid.) G. Klotz" authorityName="G. Klotz" baseAuthorityName="C. K. Schneid." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="kotschyi">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0DFFCDFB22F8DEFA985273" box="[1221,1330,1810,1837]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">C. kotschyi</emphasis>
(C. K. Schneid.) G. Klotz
</taxonomicName>
. The latter species is widely distributed in 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0DFFCDFA64F8FEFA055212" box="[1411,1455,1843,1869]" name="Iran" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0DFFCDFCD1F89FFC075233" author="RIEDL H." box="[822,941,1874,1900]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" pagination="13 - 26" refId="ref5495" refString="RIEDL H. 1969. - Cotoneaster Medik., in RECHINGER K. H. (ed.), Flora Iranica. Akademische Druck und Verlagsanstalt, Graz 66: 13 - 26." type="journal article" year="1969">Riedl 1969</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0DFFCDFC5CF89FFBC55233" author="KHATAMSAZ M." box="[955,1135,1874,1900]" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" pagination="209 - 239" refId="ref4690" refString="KHATAMSAZ M. 1992. - Cotoneaster Medik., in ASSADI M. (ed.), Flora of Iran. Research institute of forests and rangelands publication, Tehran 6: 209 - 239 [in Persian]." type="journal article" year="1992">Khatamsaz 1992</bibRefCitation>
). However, 
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0DFFCDFB16F89FFACF5233" box="[1265,1381,1874,1900]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minutus">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0DFFCDFB16F89FFACF5233" box="[1265,1381,1874,1900]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">C. minutus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from the 
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0DFFCDFC73F8BFFBAE52D3" box="[916,1028,1906,1932]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="kotschyi">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0DFFCDFC73F8BFFBAE52D3" box="[916,1028,1906,1932]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="143">C. kotschyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the small (up to 
<quantity id="4CDD9B4EEE0DFFCDFB05F8BFFA8E52D3" box="[1250,1316,1906,1932]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" unit="mm" value="7.0">7 mm</quantity>
vs 
<quantity id="4CDD9B4EEE0DFFCDFAAFF8BFFA0552D3" box="[1352,1455,1906,1932]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.4" metricValueMin="0.6" pageId="4" pageNumber="143" unit="mm" value="10.0" valueMax="14.0" valueMin="6.0">6-14 mm</quantity>
in length) and orbicular leaves (vs elliptic-ovate) and the light red fruits (vs black- purple) (
